name: first 1 row
query_template: SELECT {columns} FROM {table} WHERE ROWNUM = 1 ORDER BY {order_column} ASC

name: first 100 rows
query_template: SELECT {columns} FROM {table} WHERE ROWNUM <= 100 ORDER BY {order_column} ASC

name: first 1000 rows
query_template: SELECT {columns} FROM {table} WHERE ROWNUM <= 1000 ORDER BY {order_column} ASC

name: first 1 row
query_template: SELECT {columns} FROM {table} WHERE ROWNUM = 1 ORDER BY {order_column} DESC

name: first 100 row
query_template: SELECT {columns} FROM {table} WHERE ROWNUM <= 100 ORDER BY {order_column} DESC

name: first 1000 row
query_template: SELECT {columns} FROM {table} WHERE ROWNUM <= 1000 ORDER BY {order_column} DESC

name: DENSE_RANK
query_template: SELECT {columns}, {analytic_column}, DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY {analytic_column} ORDER BY {order_column}) FROM {table} WHERE ROWNUM <= {row}

name: RANK and DENSE_RANK
query_template: SELECT {columns}, {analytic_column}, {order_column}, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY {analytic_column} ORDER BY {order_column} DESC) AS RANK, DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY {analytic_column} ORDER BY {order_column}) AS DENSE_RANK FROM {table} WHERE ROWNUM <= {row}

name: starts with characters
query_template: SELECT {column} FROM {table} WHERE {column} LIKE 'S%' AND ROWNUM <= {row}

name: containing characters
query_template: SELECT {column} FROM {table} WHERE {column} LIKE '%s%' AND ROWNUM <= {row}
